				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="dablink">This article is about the British Broadcasting Corporation.  For other uses, see <a href="BBC_(disambiguation)" title="BBC (disambiguation)">BBC (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
<table class="infobox vcard" cellspacing="3" style="border-spacing: 3px; width:22em;">
<caption class="fn org" style="">British Broadcasting Corporation (BBC)</caption>
